Americans are angry about immigrationIt's time to face this difficult fact, understand why it's happening, and deal with it. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/americans-are-angry-about-immigration https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/americans-are-angry-about-immigrationNoah Smith Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:27:26 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg" width="1456" height="1078" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1078,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:458583,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>上图是<a href="https://smarthistory.org/seeing-america-2/nativism-and-the-know-nothing-party/">一无所知党</a>的支持者于 1850 年左右发布的漫画，该党是一个短命的美国政党，成立于 1800 年代中期，旨在反对移民。 （这个名字应该表明该党是一个秘密社团，而不是其成员是一群无知的傻瓜，尽管在后一点上你可以得出任何你喜欢的结论。）一无所知代表了美国周期性的反社会运动之一。 - 移民的强烈抵制——其他包括 1910 年代本土主义者的强烈抵制，导致了<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immigration_Act_of_1924">1924 年限制性的约翰逊-里德法案</a>，以及 1990 年代的强烈抵制，导致了<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_Responsibility_and_Work_Opportunity_Act#Provisions">1996 年一项法律</a>，使许多移民没有资格获得福利，以及十年后<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_Fence_Act_of_2006">的《安全围栏法案》</a>之后。</p><p>如果您认为美国始终是一个开放、有吸引力、对移民友好的地方，请再想一想。<em>通常</em>是这样；迄今为止的所有强烈反对最终都消退了，宽松的移民制度又回来了。我们的领导人，从乔治·华盛顿和托马斯·杰斐逊到林登·约翰逊和罗纳德·里根，几乎总是<a href="https://fordmurraylaw.com/presidential-thoughts-on-immigration/">一群支持移民的人</a>。移民在我们国家的自我概念中<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Americanism-Twenty-First-Century-Opinion-Immigration/dp/0521145244">根深蒂固</a>。但每隔一段时间，足够多的美国人就会意识到移民对我们国家构成威胁，他们会采取行动限制这种威胁。</p><p>不幸的是，现在似乎正是这样的时期之一。反移民情绪在特朗普执政期间崩溃，但在拜登领导下卷土重来： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressi