v><p>她的参考文献是<a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41567-023-02230-0">Mirletz 等人于 2023 年发表的论文。</a>关于太阳能电池板废物的论文以及<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0956053X17300491">Liu 和 Barlow 于 2017 年发表的关于风力涡轮机叶片废物的论文</a>。以下是相关图表： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg" width="688" height="388.989939637827" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ff13d78-7419-4922-9464-edddbec61609_994x562.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&q