&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8ac12b589aaf78f30217fd15eb&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E19: Singapore, Xi Jingping Cleans Up SF, &amp; Progressive Dystopias&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/3ucV725T4VMnlsL0azUv4b&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/3ucV725T4VMnlsL0azUv4b" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>这里有<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/e19-singapore-xi-jing-ping-cleans-up-sf-progressive/id1696419056?i=1000634965304">Apple 播客</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=76zsXHqA-C0">YouTube</a>的链接（如果您使用的话）。在这一集中，我们讨论新加坡、习近平对旧金山的访问，以及我关于<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/yes-its-possible-to-imagine-progressive">进步反乌托邦的</a>帖子。</p><p>无论如何，本周的至少五件有趣的事情，其中​​实际上有六件：</p><h4> 1. 实际工资是上升还是下降？</h4><p>明年，重大的经济辩论将是，在乔·拜登的领导下，美国人的生活是否会变得更好？这就是选举年的运作方式。其中一个争论将是关于实际工资是上涨还是下降，即一小时的工作是否能够为美国人提供比拜登上任前更多的鸡蛋、汽油、房租、医疗保健等。</p><p>答案很复杂。首先，这取决于你的比较点。实际每小时薪酬（包括工资和福利）为：</p><ul><li><p>高于疫情前，</p></li><li><p>低于大流行前的趋势线，</p></li><li><p>较 2021 年初拜登上任时有所下降，并且</p></li><li><p>从 2022 年中期开始。</p></li></ul><p>这是这四种比较的图表： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:1318,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:39256,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f40535-b180-4a4a-9ff4-17024c02e337_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>显然，您认为这些比较中哪一个更重要将取决于<s>您在 TikTok 上看到的最后一个视频、</s>您的政治观点和您的个人经济状况。</p><p>但事实上，由于两个原因，事情变得更加复杂：</p><ol><li><p>典型工人的工资与平均工资不同，因为高层人员（首席执行官和人工智能工程师等）的非常高的工资会使平均数字出现很大偏差。</p></li><li><p>这场大流行导致低工资工人以不成比例的比例被解雇，这机械地提高了平均水平，远高于保住工作的人的工资涨幅。</p></li></ol><p>劳工经济学家阿林·杜贝（Arin Dube）将其中第一个放在图表中，向我们展示了生产工人和非管理工人的每小时收入比总体平均水平要好得多： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg" width="1343" height="895" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:895,&quot;width&quot;:1343,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:210579,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79271b40-10a6-406e-9220-cc1a0c3ecada_1343x895.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/arindube/status/1722695167013236744">阿林·杜贝</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>（注：每小时收入与每小时薪酬有些不同，因为薪酬包括医疗保健付款和退休金等福利。）</p><p>至于构图效果，评估起来要困难得多。乔伊·波利塔诺（Joey Politano）有<a href="https://www.apricitas.io/p/are-real-wages-rising">一篇很好的博客文章</a>，讨论了各种工资指标，他指出，当你保持工作构成不变时，工资实际上比标题数字<em>更糟糕</em>。下面是实际就业成本指数的图表，该指数根据工作构成进行调整，并与实际每小时薪酬进行比较： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:1318,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:63215,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6148492-e9c7-4c51-b328-067cf89fe8b1_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但正如波利塔诺指出的那样，这也可能具有欺骗性。自大流行以来的几年里，许多美国人已经从低薪工作转向高薪工作，这是好事，就业成本指数将完全忽略这一点。</p><p>总的来说，我们的情况好坏参半。实际工资再次增长，这是好事，而且对于中层和底层的人来说，工资增长得更快，这也是好事。但他们在 2021 年和 2022 年遭受的巨大打击尚未完全消除。</p><h4> 2.朝鲜为什么这么穷？</h4><p>我很偶然地发现，让推特上的左派人士生气的一个简单方法就是发布一张朝鲜半岛夜间的图片。这篇文章顶部著名的那个现在已经很老了，但是还有<a href="https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=583077499&amp;rlz=1C1RXQR_enUS1011US1011&amp;sxsrf=AM9HkKmVfeG2qS75l6s2dBckyoTYEGMIaw:1700164283473&amp;q=north+korea+at+night&amp;tbm=isch&amp;source=lnms&amp;sa=X&amp;sqi=2&amp;ved=2ahUKEwifgrTBpcmCAxXrLEQIHQutAvIQ0pQJegQICRAB&amp;biw=1536&amp;bih=739&amp;dpr=1.25#imgrc=4SHjkpEdZqL0DM">很多其他的</a>，是的，它看起来仍然像那样。朝鲜是<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-41228181">一个极其贫穷的国家</a>，而韩国是一个极其富裕的国家。这个事实经常被用来证明共产主义是坏的，资本主义是好的。</p><p>但朝鲜究竟为何如此贫穷？古巴和苏联都是共产主义国家，而且它们比朝鲜贫穷得多。近年来，中国和越南等名义上的“共产主义”政权经历了快速发展，而朝鲜却没有。有什么不同？</p><p>左派人士喜爱的一种解释是，美国只是将朝鲜轰炸回了 70 年前的石器时代，朝鲜就一直留在那里。这不可信。即使你认为对朝鲜的轰炸比对韩国的破坏更具破坏性（韩国首都在战争期间三度易手），但它仍然不符合朝鲜的时间表。事实上，直到 20 世纪 70 年代初，朝鲜一直<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_North_Korea#Economic_development">在以不错的速度增长</a>，并与韩国保持同步。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg" width="646" height="433.3718592964824" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:534,&quot;width&quot;:796,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:646,&quot;bytes&quot;:36782,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F650ad3b5-5687-4395-9277-30689a85750f_796x534.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：麦迪逊项目，来自<a href="https://tino.us/2010/06/north-korean-economic-history/">Tino Sanandaji</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>显然这些数字很难准确地知道，而1973年至1992年间朝鲜的完美直线只是意味着“我们没有这一时期的任何数据”。但在 1965 年，经济学家琼·罗宾逊 (Joan Robinson) 赞扬了朝鲜的快速经济增长和成功的重建工作：</p><blockquote><p>十一年前，在平江，没有一块石头压在另一块石头上。 （他们估计每人投下一吨或更多的炸弹。）现在，一座拥有一百万居民的现代化城市矗立在宽阔的河流两侧，宽阔的五层楼街道两旁绿树成荫，公共建筑、体育场、剧院（其中一个地下剧院在战争中幸存）和一家超豪华酒店。工业部门包括许多现代化的纺织厂和纺织机械厂。宽阔的河流和被保留为公园的绿树成荫的小山提供了宜人的景色。有一些用瓦砾匆忙建造的灰色和白色的小房子，但即使在那里，小巷也很干净，有灯光和水。一个没有贫民窟的城市。</p></blockquote><p>那么20世纪70年代发生了什么？一方面，朝鲜开始<a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/2644123">大规模军备建设</a>，以减少对俄罗斯和中国的军事依赖。这转移了对民用经济投资的资源。朝鲜还从国际上借了一大笔钱，并<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_North_Korea#Later_years_of_Kim_Il-sung_(1970s%E2%80%931994)">大力投资采矿业</a>；上世纪70年代、80年代、90年代，它因金属价格长期下跌而遭受重创，无力偿还外债，不得不违约。再加上1991年苏联的解体——苏联向朝鲜提供了大量援助和贸易——造成了长期的宏观经济冲击，需要很长时间才能恢复。</p><p>当然，这是典型的共产主义对微观经济管理不善的表现。朝鲜一直是世界上最<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economy_of_North_Korea#State_Planning_Commission">集中的计划</a>经济体之一；极端的中央计划有利于发动战争或从战争中重建，但否则往往会严重错误分配资源。中央计划有一定的最佳水平，而朝鲜只是超出了它。 <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juche">“主体”（自力更生）原则</a>也阻止朝鲜出口制成品（这是韩国提高生产力和致富的主要方式之一）和进口本可以用作国内生产投入的商品。</p><p>西方制裁也是朝鲜经济孤立的一个因素，但可能没有人们想象的那么严重。大多数制裁<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_sanctions_against_North_Korea">都是最近才实施的</a>，并且是由于该国的核计划；此前，朝鲜实际上出口了大量矿产品。与此同时，中国没有实施制裁，事实上与朝鲜进行了<a href="https://nautilus.org/napsnet/napsnet-special-reports/dprk-prc-trade-aden/">大量</a>贸易，但由于中国的重商主义政策和朝鲜总体工业落后，朝鲜存在巨额贸易逆差，而且大多只向中国出售矿产。与此同时，朝鲜普遍<a href="https://www.reuters.com/article/us-korea-north-kaesong/north-korea-cancels-deal-with-south-on-factory-park-idUSTRE54E0IR20090515/">抵制韩国扩大经济联系的努力</a>。</p><p>换句话说，朝鲜的贫困确实不难解释。当你是一个小国，你封闭自己的贸易并故意对国内经济管理不善时，你就会变得贫穷。如果美国能够向朝鲜伸出援手，帮助其摆脱偏执，情况可能会改变。这不太可能，但<a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/09/10/fact-sheet-president-joseph-r-biden-and-general-secretary-nguyen-phu-trong-announce-the-u-s-vietnam-comprehensive-strategic-partnership/">我们刚刚在越南做到了这一点</a>，所以也许还有希望。</p><h4> 3.中国经济真的落后于美国吗？</h4><p>围绕亚太经合组织峰会 <a href="https://www.wsj.com/economy/why-xi-can-no-longer-brag-about-the-chinese-economy-3397e6f4">，美国在经济上充满了必胜的信念</a>。总的来说，我认为这是有一定道理的；美国经济表现出色，而中国经济则陷入困境。但很多人都在分享这张中国 GDP 相对于美国 GDP 的图表，作为中国经济追赶已经停止的证据： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F663af280-f4f0-40a2-a217-e63df24b8922_620x500.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F663af280-f4f0-40a2-a217-e63df24b8922_620x500.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.